<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FutureX Skills 知识库</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=LXGW+WenKai:wght@300;400;700&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ===== Design Tokens ===== */
:root {
  --color-ink: #1a1a2e;
  --color-ink-light: #2d2d44;
  --color-ink-muted: #5a5a7a;
  --color-navy: #002958;
  --color-navy-light: #1a4080;
  --color-gold: #c9a84c;
  --color-gold-light: #f0d78c;
  --color-gold-bg: #fdf8ec;
  --color-vermillion: #c84b31;
  --color-sage: #6b8f71;
  --color-sage-light: #d4e4d6;
  --color-ivory: #faf6ee;
  --color-paper: #f3ece0;
  --color-paper-deep: #e8dcc8;
  --color-white: #fffcf7;
  --color-terminal-bg: #1a1a2e;
  --color-terminal-text: #d4d4d4;

  --font-display: 'Noto Serif SC', 'Songti SC', serif;
  --font-body: 'LXGW WenKai', 'Kaiti SC', serif;
  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;

  --space-xs: 0.5rem;
  --space-sm: 1rem;
  --space-md: 2rem;
  --space-lg: 4rem;
  --space-xl: 6rem;
  --space-2xl: 10rem;

  --max-width: 1200px;
  --border-thin: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.1);
  --shadow-card: 0 4px 24px rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.08);
  --shadow-lifted: 0 12px 40px rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.12);
}

/* ===== Reset ===== */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
body {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  color: var(--color-ink);
  background-color: var(--color-ivory);
  line-height: 1.8;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(0, 41, 88, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}
body::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 24px 24px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* ===== Animations ===== */
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
.reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; } }

/* ===== Layout ===== */
.container { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-md); position: relative; z-index: 1; }
section { padding: var(--space-xl) 0; }
.divider { width: 100%; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(26,26,46,0.12) 20%, rgba(201,168,76,0.25) 50%, rgba(26,26,46,0.12) 80%, transparent); }

/* ===== Typography ===== */
.section-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-vermillion); margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); font-weight: 500; }
.section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.25; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
.section-subtitle { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); max-width: 580px; line-height: 1.9; }

/* ================================================
   HERO
   ================================================ */
.hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: var(--space-xl) 0; }
.hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -20%; right: -5%; width: 700px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,41,88,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; }
.hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -15%; left: -5%; width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; }

.hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hero-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-vermillion); letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); }
.hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--color-vermillion); }
.hero-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.08; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
.hero-title span { display: block; color: var(--color-navy); }
.hero-tagline { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem); color: var(--color-ink-light); max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); line-height: 2; }
.hero-metrics { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-md); }
.metric-value { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--color-ink); line-height: 1.2; }
.metric-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-top: 2px; }

.hero-stamp { position: absolute; right: 6%; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; opacity: 0.06; pointer-events: none; }
.hero-stamp span { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--color-navy); writing-mode: vertical-rl; line-height: 1; }

/* ================================================
   STATS BAR
   ================================================ */
.stats-bar { background: var(--color-navy); padding: var(--space-md) 0; }
.stats-bar-inner { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: var(--space-xl); flex-wrap: wrap; }
.stats-bar-item { text-align: center; color: white; }
.stats-bar-num { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--color-gold); }
.stats-bar-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-top: 2px; }

/* ================================================
   ARCHITECTURE
   ================================================ */
.arch-section { background: var(--color-white); border-top: var(--border-thin); border-bottom: var(--border-thin); }
.arch-diagram { margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-sm); }
.arch-layer { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-md); padding: var(--space-md); border-radius: 8px; background: var(--color-ivory); border-left: 4px solid transparent; transition: box-shadow 0.3s; }
.arch-layer:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
.arch-layer--navy { border-left-color: var(--color-navy); }
.arch-layer--vermillion { border-left-color: var(--color-vermillion); }
.arch-layer--gold { border-left-color: var(--color-gold); }
.arch-layer--sage { border-left-color: var(--color-sage); }
.arch-layer-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }
.arch-layer-count { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
.arch-layer-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: 1.7; }

/* ================================================
   CATALOG
   ================================================ */
.catalog-section { padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
.catalog-layer { margin-top: var(--space-lg); }
.catalog-layer-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); padding-bottom: var(--space-xs); border-bottom: var(--border-thin); }
.catalog-layer-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.catalog-layer-dot--navy { background: var(--color-navy); }
.catalog-layer-dot--vermillion { background: var(--color-vermillion); }
.catalog-layer-dot--gold { background: var(--color-gold); }
.catalog-layer-dot--sage { background: var(--color-sage); }
.catalog-layer-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }
.catalog-layer-badge { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); background: var(--color-paper); padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 100px; }

.skills-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-sm); }

.skill-card { background: var(--color-white); border: var(--border-thin); border-radius: 8px; padding: var(--space-md); transition: box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.2s; cursor: pointer; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.skill-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); transform: translateY(-2px); }

.skill-card-header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: var(--space-xs); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.skill-card-name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-vermillion); }
.skill-card-version { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }
.skill-card-zh { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.skill-card-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-light); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }

.skill-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; }
.tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 100px; background: var(--color-paper); color: var(--color-ink-muted); white-space: nowrap; }
.tag.ext { background: var(--color-sage-light); color: #3d6b44; }
.tag.team { background: var(--color-gold-bg); color: #8b6914; }
.tag.gpilot { background: #fff3d0; color: #a06000; }

.skill-card-footer { margin-top: var(--space-sm); padding-top: var(--space-sm); border-top: var(--border-thin); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.skill-card-source { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); }
.skill-card-link { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-navy); font-weight: 500; }
.skill-card-link::after { content: ' →'; opacity: 0.5; }

/* ================================================
   EXTERNAL SECTION
   ================================================ */
.ext-section { background: var(--color-white); border-top: var(--border-thin); border-bottom: var(--border-thin); }

.sub-group { margin-top: var(--space-lg); }
.sub-group:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.sub-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.sub-title a { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-vermillion); font-weight: 400; }
.sub-title a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* ================================================
   WORKFLOWS (Navigation)
   ================================================ */
.nav-section { background: var(--color-navy); color: white; }
.nav-grid { margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-sm); }
.nav-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 8px; padding: var(--space-md); transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; cursor: pointer; }
.nav-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.nav-card-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.nav-card-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.nav-card-count { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.nav-card-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6; }

/* ================================================
   FOOTER
   ================================================ */
footer { padding: var(--space-lg) 0; text-align: center; color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: var(--border-thin); }
footer a { color: var(--color-vermillion); text-decoration: none; }
footer .seal { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--color-navy); opacity: 0.15; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }

/* ================================================
   RESPONSIVE
   ================================================ */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .arch-layer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero-stamp { display: none; }
  .stats-bar-inner { gap: var(--space-md); }
  .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .hero-metrics { gap: var(--space-sm); }
  section { padding: var(--space-lg) 0; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ==================== HERO ==================== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow reveal">FUTUREX CAPITAL</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title reveal reveal-delay-1">FutureX<br><span>Skills 知识库</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline reveal reveal-delay-2">天际资本 AI Skills 资产沉淀仓库，涵盖投研、内容创作、运营提效等全场景智能体工具集。全部开源，供创业者和行业同行免费使用。</p>
      <div class="hero-metrics reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div>
          <div class="metric-value" data-target="26">0</div>
          <div class="metric-label">天际内部 Skills</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="metric-value" data-target="28">0</div>
          <div class="metric-label">外部精选 Skills</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="metric-value" data-target="1">0</div>
          <div class="metric-label">CEO 开源项目</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="metric-value" data-target="55">0</div>
          <div class="metric-label">Skills 合计</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stamp" aria-hidden="true"><span>天</span></div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ==================== STATS BAR ==================== -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-bar-inner">
      <div class="stats-bar-item"><div class="stats-bar-num">26</div><div class="stats-bar-label">天际团队自建 Skills</div></div>
      <div class="stats-bar-item"><div class="stats-bar-num">28</div><div class="stats-bar-label">外部精选收录</div></div>
      <div class="stats-bar-item"><div class="stats-bar-num">1</div><div class="stats-bar-label">GPilot-Simon</div></div>
      <div class="stats-bar-item"><div class="stats-bar-num">100%</div><div class="stats-bar-label">完全开源</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ==================== ARCHITECTURE ==================== -->
<section class="arch-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label reveal">ARCHITECTURE</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">三层架构</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">天际 Skills 分为三大类：团队自建、外部精选、CEO 开源项目。</p>

    <div class="arch-diagram">
      <div class="arch-layer arch-layer--navy reveal">
        <div>
          <div class="arch-layer-name">天际团队SKills库</div>
          <div class="arch-layer-count">26 skills · 内部自建</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-layer-desc">天际资本团队在实际投资业务、内容创作、运营提效中打磨出的 Skills，覆盖投研尽调、内容生产、运营合规等全场景。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-layer arch-layer--vermillion reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div>
          <div class="arch-layer-name">外部精选Skills</div>
          <div class="arch-layer-count">28 skills · 社区精选</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-layer-desc">天际主动发掘和评测来自社区的优质开源 Skills，将其收入外部精选库推荐给大家，包括李继刚认知工具集、43-Agent-skills 等。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-layer arch-layer--gold reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div>
          <div class="arch-layer-name">GPilot-Simon</div>
          <div class="arch-layer-count">CEO 开源项目 · 独立展示</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-layer-desc">天际资本 CEO Simon 独立开发的多智能体投资管理系统，是本知识库的技术底座。面向 VC/PE 投资人的 AI 原生工作流框架。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ==================== SKILLS CATALOG: 团队 ==================== -->
<section class="catalog-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label reveal">CATALOG</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">天际团队SKills库</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">26 个团队自建 Skills，点击直接跳转 GitHub 仓库。</p>

    <div class="catalog-layer">
      <div class="catalog-layer-header reveal">
        <div class="catalog-layer-dot catalog-layer-dot--navy"></div>
        <div class="catalog-layer-title">天际团队SKills库</div>
        <div class="catalog-layer-badge">26 skills</div>
      </div>
      <div class="skills-grid">

        <div class="skill-card reveal" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/FutureX-Skills/FutureX-SKills/tree/main/%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%85%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9FSkills%E5%BA%93/%E7%A0%94%E6%8A%A5%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B','_blank')">
          <div class="skill-card-header"><span class="skill-card-name">研报助手</span><span class="skill-card-version">MoE</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-zh">研报助手</div>
          <div class="skill-card-desc">MoE 多智能体调度中心，生成投行级尽调报告。技术审计、财务精算、红队战略三 Agent 协作。</div>
          <div class="skill-card-tags"><span class="tag team">投研</span><span class="tag team">尽调</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-footer"><span class="skill-card-source">天际内部</span><span class="skill-card-link">GitHub</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-1" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/FutureX-Skills/FutureX-SKills/tree/main/%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%85%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9FSkills%E5%BA%93/GPilot-Simon','_blank')">
          <div class="skill-card-header"><span class="skill-card-name">GPilot-Simon</span><span class="skill-card-version">CEO</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-zh">GPilot-Simon</div>
          <div class="skill-card-desc">CEO Simon 多智能体投资管理系统。8个专用Agent、19个投研命令、9个定时任务、Next.js管理面板。</div>
          <div class="skill-card-tags"><span class="tag gpilot">CEO开源</span><span class="tag gpilot">多Agent</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-footer"><span class="skill-card-source">独立展示</span><span class="skill-card-link">GitHub</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-card reveal" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/FutureX-Skills/FutureX-SKills/tree/main/%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%85%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9FSkills%E5%BA%93/%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88','_blank')">
          <div class="skill-card-header"><span class="skill-card-name">视频标题大师</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-zh">视频标题大师</div>
          <div class="skill-card-desc">短视频封面标题与简介生成，支持抖音、视频号、小红书等平台，25个多风格标题方案。</div>
          <div class="skill-card-tags"><span class="tag team">内容</span><span class="tag team">短视频</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-footer"><span class="skill-card-source">天际内部</span><span class="skill-card-link">GitHub</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-1" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/FutureX-Skills/FutureX-SKills/tree/main/%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%85%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9FSkills%E5%BA%93/%E7%A1%8E%E8%B0%B7%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A','_blank')">
          <div class="skill-card-header"><span class="skill-card-name">硅谷季度报告</span></div>
          <div class="skill-card-zh">硅谷季度报告</div>
          <div class="skill-card-desc">VC 赛道趋势分析报告，追踪过去 90 天投资格局变化、技术范式转移、产业动态。</div>
          <div class="skill-card-tags"><span class="tag team">投研</span><span class="tag team">赛道分析</span></div>
